Package: HDcox
Title: High Dimensional Cox
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Pedro", "Salguero Garcia", , "pedrosalguerog@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1879-3374"))
Description: Cox analysis for high dimensional data. HDcox proportionate a serie of classical cox and (s)PLS-COX functions to manage and work with high dimensional data sets. Furthermore, cross validation, plots, and extra functions for the understanding of the results are provided.
